<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٠-<span style="color:#006d98"> قَالَ:</span> وَسَمِعْتُ يَحْيَى يَقُولُ:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>أَخُوكَ مَنْ عَرَّفَكَ الْعُيُوبَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَصَدِيقُكُ مَنْ حَذَّرَكَ الذُّنُوبَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>